fields.name: EncryptionAlgorithm
fields.description: Encryption algorithm that will be used along with this client encryption key to encrypt/decrypt data.

fields.name: Etag
fields.description: A system generated property representing the resource etag required for optimistic concurrency control.

fields.name: KeyWrapMetadata
fields.description: Metadata for the wrapping provider that can be used to unwrap the wrapped client encryption key.

fields.name: Rid
fields.description: A system generated property. A unique identifier.

fields.name: Ts
fields.description: A system generated property that denotes the last updated timestamp of the resource.

fields.name: WrappedDataEncryptionKey
fields.description: Wrapped (encrypted) form of the key represented as a byte array.
